5.000Z","msg":"人都係"},{"pid":"7a3d60f8e8a067c8b3c7111fe734bf06bc742fea","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人都係</blockquote><br />\n咁專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3413f5cf995fab85b49dbaa43bd7c299d69ef10f","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>M記多醬巨無霸</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我個名都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38270af2e8febc57fd9e8b895a0a9cc40b8417a","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔係日日食 但去親嗰間餐廳只係會食嗰一樣野算唔算上癮</blockquote><br />\n 會唔會隔兩日就會想食</blockquote><br />\n一個禮拜左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想食嘅野比較多 輪住食 無乜試新野</blockquote><br />\n星期一譚仔 星期二雲貴香 星期三脆香雞翼 如此類推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ddb7c8acf0867b9e316b4ce880e401a3284ec6","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣去某餐廳就九成九嗌某餐廳最喜歡果一樣野（多數果啲餐廳不常去）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打唔符合資格"},{"pid":"4da2c8ebaebc18f8704715451c90c249ce2babb7","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">食</span>開就唔想試其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但俾人話固執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我比人話我痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我男朋友唔鐘意我食個啲 所以同佢一齊就變左食其他野 自己個陣通常都係食翻個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611d387b241ca9c5c6a50d9b10a3bb1d599c77ba","tid":245534,"uid":64067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:50:00.000Z","msg":"鳳爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4c2e40016b46ec8476292455230421b55887b0","tid":245534,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2706110896a2200cd0c090f9e55b562bd5fd47d","tid":245534,"uid":14340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"魚香茄子！"},{"pid":"f06f76db144f6b792f6104badbd54459c0877d43","tid":245534,"uid":39218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"吉野家下午茶<br />\n玉子牛飯牛汁凍檸走冰<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前食開玉子雞但冇左唯有轉牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7414cfc0590678efc0b350026e0898684f884550","tid":245534,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"薯仔同沙律 真係食多多都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d1317f597ecc098a34cb7f5d216d0a6c3bec6d","tid":245534,"uid":13521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吉野家下午茶<br />\n玉子牛飯牛汁凍檸走冰<br />\n<br />\n利申：以前食開玉子雞但冇左唯有轉牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吉野家我淨係打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}